  <brief_title>Study of VIR-2218 With or Without Pegylated Interferon Alpha-2a for Treatment of Chronic Hepatitis B Virus Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1/2 Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, and Antiviral Activity of VIR-2218 Alone or in Combination With Pegylated Interferon Alpha-2a</official_title>
